HEADWORD: Fading
<hw>Fad"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An Irish dance; also, the burden of
a song.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Fading</xex> is a fine jig.⟦rdquo⟧
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Beau. & Fl.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
